snippet.title: NARUTO TO BORUTO: SHINOBI STRIKER - Class Type Trailer | PS4, X1, PC
snippet.description:
Time to craft your team in NARUTO TO BORUTO: SHINOBI STRIKER!  Get ready to combine the skills of Attack, Ranged, Heal, and Defense to tackle any challenge. Deal massive amounts of damage with attack, fight enemies from afar as ranged, protect your team as defense, or make support your teammates to continue the battle as Heal!

Prepare to represent your Hidden Village! NARUTO TO BORUTO: SHINOBI STRIKER launches August 31st for PS4, X1, and Steam! Pre-order your copy today! https://bandainam.co/shinobistrikerbuy
